Technical illustration: Four chunking strategies side by side. 1) Fixed-Size: Rectangle divided into equal blocks, red warning at boundaries. 2) Recursive: Hierarchical splitting - paragraphs -> sentences -> words, green checkmarks. 3) Markdown/Header: Document with heading hierarchy preserved as metadata tags. 4) Code: Python code split at function/class boundaries. Minimalist technical style, blue/green/red color coding for good/bad/neutral.